27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Suns\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.031626082439881e-31, \"text\": \"Phoenix Suns\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Suns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Suns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was cleared to play ahead of Team USA's first group stage game against Nikola Jokic's Serbia squad.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999992297137634, \"rank\": 7.701017536949184e-07, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Joki\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9999999949418452, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nikola Jokic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Joki\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Joki\\u0107\"}, {\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.988405822766626, \"rank\": 0.011725281920122555, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Durant did not start but came in pretty quickly off the bench andimmediatelycaught fire.\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He wasted zero time in making his impact felt.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Durant went 4-for-4 from the field to start his shift, including 3-for-3 from deep, and gave a big grin to Team USA's bench after his fourth consecutive make.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999992297137634, \"rank\": 7.701017536949184e-07, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was, as the kids say, feeling himself.\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's Durant's first bucket\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 as automatic as we all remember.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kevin Durant is BACK.pic.twitter.com/jjfiKpE0ob  And here's his fourth make, featuring a wide smile.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 0.9999972091948456, \"rank\": 2.7908125842219742e-06, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EASY MONEY SNIPER \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0094\\u00a5Kevin Durant looks UNSTOPPABLE in his Team USA debut \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8pic.twitter.com/87uF49pOjG  Durant is just a hooper and there are few players in the history of basketball with a jumper as smooth as his.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unstoppable_(2010_film)\", \"score\": 0.9693374377691075, \"rank\": 0.017365350698688345, \"text\": \"UNSTOPPABLE\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unstoppable_(2010_film)\", \"dbpedia\